        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "MUST-HAVE: Either (1) increase visibility timeout to at least 60s (2x worst-case batch time), (2) process messages with individual ack after each completes rather than after full batch, or (3) implement idempotency keys. Ideally all three."
